<h1>Help</h1>

<p>Welcome to the Help page of our application. Here, you can find answers to commonly asked questions and get assistance with using our application.</p>

<h3>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h3>

<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Q: How do I add a task to my to-do list?</strong><br>
        A: To add a task to your to-do list, go to the "Tasks" page and click on the "Add Task" button. Fill in the task details, such as title, description, and due date, and click "Save" to add the task to your to-do list.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Q: How do I mark a task as completed?</strong><br>
        A: To mark a task as completed, go to the "Tasks" page and click on the checkbox next to the task you want to mark as completed. The task will be marked as completed and moved to the "Completed" tasks section.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Q: How do I edit or delete a task?</strong><br>
        A: To edit or delete a task, go to the "Tasks" page and click on the "Edit" or "Delete" button next to the task you want to edit or delete. You can update the task details in the edit form or click "Delete" to remove the task from your to-do list.
    </li>
